{"tid":91471,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"其實賣唔出既寵物都係送去毀滅","createTime":"2017-01-23T01:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T16:27:09.000Z","uid":4959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36be39ad62fa36006037b0f4261f12eafad8f29a","tid":91471,"uid":4959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T01:24:51.000Z","msg":"賣唔出既貓狗過左某一個年紀或者大細，其實都會送去人道毀滅，貓狗義工有無諗過成日叫人領養其實都係害緊另一方既動物？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc9857f4a5bcda0b02601b614f90ab27f7b0dac","tid":91471,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T01:26:24.000Z","msg":"做低啲寵物店 破壞惡性循環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9e0da57ddbcaaabbfccda098e6b5ae47634e5c","tid":91471,"uid":4959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T03:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fe4f8d0117959f8e74d157db1f7bef07a05080","tid":91471,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T03:39:20.000Z","msg":"其實啱㗎 如果真係咁大愛 就應該拯救晒所有動物 買返去再畀人領養？定畀人送去人道毀滅 啲義工去領養 再畀人領養？<br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句 義工嘅宗旨莫過於拯救無人要嘅小動物 幫佢哋搵到個家 唔好助長啲寵物店 因為寵物店嗰啲通常都有病 大陸狗 近親繁殖 ...<br />\n<br />\n無論領養定買 都希望主人有返個責任心<br />\n我知好多人都追求品種 真係講眼緣 或者領養唔到啱心水先買 領養定買 都唔係100%保證佢健康無病無痛 只係你心靈上覺得幫咗啲小動物 但學樓主講咁 你領養一隻 但救唔到另一邊 其實都好矛盾 ... <br />\n<br />\n但希望無論買又好 領養又好 佢有病 就唔好遺棄佢 照顧佢一生一世 ..."},{"pid":"f659f544634aa8700af3b7fd4a1f4a6e965acf8c","tid":91471,"uid":4959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:27:09.000Z","msg":"居然無大愛撚反駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}